name: DOCS_RCVD_OB_HX_PREG
description: OB History table for pregnancy data.

columns.name: DOCUMENT_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the document record.

columns.name: CONTACT_DATE_REAL
columns.description: A unique contact date in decimal format. The integer portion of the number indicates the date of contact. The digits after the decimal distinguish different contacts on the same date and are unique for each contact on that date. For example, .00 is the first/only contact, .01 is the second contact, etc.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this contact. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this contact.

columns.name: CONTACT_DATE
columns.description: The date of this contact in calendar format.

columns.name: PREG_ID
columns.description: Unique identifier for an individual pregnancy. Used to link pregnancies to delivery lines.

columns.name: HISTORICAL_YN
columns.description: Whether a pregnancy is historical.

columns.name: OUTCM_DT_FUZINESS_C_NAME
columns.description: The fuzziness/confidence of an outcome date in OB history.

columns.name: LAST_DEL_GA
columns.description: Gestational age in days for the last delivery for the pregnancy, based on OB History documentation.

columns.name: LAST_DEL_UTC_DTTM
columns.description: Instant of the last delivery for the pregnancy.

columns.name: NUM_FETUSES
columns.description: Total number of fetuses involved in this pregnancy

columns.name: ABORTION_COUNT
columns.description: Abortion count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: ECTOPIC_COUNT
columns.description: Ectopic count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: GRAVIDA_COUNT
columns.description: Gravida count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: PARA_COUNT
columns.description: Para count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: PRETERM_COUNT
columns.description: Preterm count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: SPONT_ABORT_COUNT
columns.description: Spontaneous abortion count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: TERM_COUNT
columns.description: Term count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: INDUCED_ABORT_COUNT
columns.description: Therapeutic abortion count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: LIVE_BIRTH_COUNT
columns.description: Live birth count prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: PREGRAVID_BMI
columns.description: Patient's body mass index prior to pregnancy.

columns.name: PRIOR_CESAREAN_YN
columns.description: Whether the patient had a cesarean delivery prior to this pregnancy.

columns.name: WORKING_EDD_DATE
columns.description: Working estimated date of delivery for the pregnancy.

columns.name: EP_START_DATE
columns.description: Start date of the pregnancy episode.

columns.name: EP_END_DATE
columns.description: End date of the pregnancy episode.

columns.name: FETAL_DEMISE_COUNT
columns.description: Count of fetal demise outcomes prior to this pregnancy.
